}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "AP-MT0D-0001", "REV1.0" and "1606" is silkscreened on the board.
Future support may be available with {{TPFirmware|Padavan}} ? ([http://forum.ixbt.com/topic.cgi?id=14:63903:3389#3389 WiP]) :The bootloader used is assumed to be '''U-Boot'''. Default SSIDs are per the manual.
